    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this adventure you are responsible for managing a Generation Ship with the mission to explore Orion's Belt. Take care of the ship and its crew and don't run out of resources but also don't let anything go beyond maximum capacity! Complet the tasks and visit the planets in search of materials to help you in your amazing space exploration!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Explore four star systems!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rigel, Alnitak, Alnilam and Mintaka!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Land on the planets and moons of these systems in search of resources!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use resources to make upgrades to your ship! Like cargo capacity or energy capacity!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Explore various types of planets and moons!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Metallic worlds, rocky worlds, icy worlds, planetary rings and Earth-like worlds!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Don't take more resources than your ship can handle, or the tripulation may end up revolting!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Always check the ship's status to make sure everything is normal!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Walk around your ship looking for tasks!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If your ship is in good condition, jump to another star system!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p>",
